Reclusa::

She looked at Hydras and smiled. She stood before him in a regal and
dominant stance.  She was one to never back down, and it showed even
in her small and slender frame. "I am pleased to meet you. Perceptor
here was a bold and knowledgable warrior. I was glad you had sent
him."  She took a step forward and put her hand out to be shook as per
a graciuos guest. "I am glad to join you here. I hope you will find my
services just as valuable as Perceptor's here."  Her tone of voice
almost had a tone of royal smugness. But still soft and melodious.
